sequenceDiagram
  participant B as Browser HMI
  participant H as HMI Backend
  participant S as SCADA Master
  participant R as RTU Simulator
  participant A as Attacker

  B->>H: GET /api/status
  H->>S: GET /api/status
  S->>R: READ_TELEMETRY
  R-->>S: TELEMETRY_RESPONSE
  S-->>H: status JSON
  H-->>B: status JSON

  B->>H: POST /api/commands/breaker/open
  H->>S: POST /api/commands/breaker/open
  S->>S: create correlation_id
  S->>R: SELECT_BREAKER
  R-->>S: COMMAND_RESPONSE select_token
  S->>R: EXECUTE_BREAKER with select_token + correlation_id
  R-->>S: COMMAND_RESPONSE accepted, detections=[]

  A->>R: EXECUTE_BREAKER OPEN claiming scada-master / SCADA_MASTER
  Note over R: Missing valid select_token and SCADA workflow correlation
  R-->>A: COMMAND_RESPONSE accepted in vulnerable mode
  S->>R: EVENT_LOG_REQUEST
  R-->>S: breaker event with RTU-side detections
  S->>S: correlate event with local command records
  S-->>B: HMI shows breaker OPEN, alarm, and SCADA detections
